---
title: Ssamjang-Glazed Beef Brisket with Garlic Rice & Cheesy Bacon Sweetcorn
description: We've taken all the fuss out of this feast and injected loads of shining flavour with our Korean-inspired Ssamjang-glazed beef
brisket that's already been slow-cooked to tender perfection. Fill the dinner table with all the fixings of aromatic rice, baked jjcheesy bacon and sweetcorn and sautéed Asian greens to complete tonight's star protein.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ssamjang-glazed-beef-brisket-84c219e6.jpg
